snippet.title: Dust: An Elysian Tail - XBLA Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Dust: An Elysian Tail, a side-scrolling action-RPG created single handedly by Dean Dodrill with music by HyperDuck Studios, is coming to XBox Live Arcade in 2012 courtesy of Microsoft!
(c) 2010 Humble Hearts, LLC
Official Website:  http://www.elysiantail.com
